<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
  <style>
    @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+KR:wght@500;700;900&display=swap');
    body { font-family: 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif; }
  </style>
</head>
<body class="bg-gray-50">
  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 py-8">
    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-start md:items-center gap-4 mb-10">
      <div>
        <h1 class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-gray-900 tracking-tight">가치 랭킹 TOP 50</h1>
        <p class="text-gray-500 mt-1">검색된 모든 브롤러 중 가장 높은 가치를 지닌 계정들입니다.</p>
      </div>
      <a href="/" class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 bg-blue-600 text-white rounded-xl font-bold hover:bg-blue-700 transition-all shadow-lg shadow-blue-200">
        내 계정 가치 측정하기
      </a>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-white rounded-3xl border border-gray-100 shadow-xl shadow-gray-50 overflow-hidden">
      <div class="overflow-x-auto">
        <table class="w-full text-left border-collapse">
          <thead>
            <tr class="bg-gray-50/50 border-b border-gray-100">
              <th class="px-8 py-5 text-xs font-bold text-gray-400 uppercase tracking-wider text-center">순위</th>
              <th class="px-8 py-5 text-xs font-bold text-gray-400 uppercase tracking-wider">플레이어</th>
              <th class="px-8 py-5 text-xs font-bold text-gray-400 uppercase tracking-wider text-right">계정 가치</th>
              <th class="px-8 py-5 text-xs font-bold text-gray-400 uppercase tracking-wider text-right">트로피</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody class="divide-y divide-gray-50">
            <% @rankers.each_with_index do |account, index| %>
              <tr class="group hover:bg-blue-50/30 transition-colors">
                <td class="px-8 py-6 text-center">
                  <% if index < 3 %>
                    <span class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-8 h-8 rounded-full <%= index == 0 ? 'bg-yellow-100 text-yellow-600' : (index == 1 ? 'bg-gray-200 text-gray-500' : 'bg-orange-100 text-orange-600') %> font-black text-sm">
                      <%= index + 1 %>
                    </span>
                  <% else %>
                    <span class="text-gray-400 font-medium"><%= index + 1 %></span>
                  <% end %>
                </td>
                <td class="px-8 py-6">
                  <div class="flex flex-col">
                    <span class="font-bold text-gray-900 group-hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors"><%= account.name %></span>
                    <span class="text-xs text-gray-400 font-mono"><%= account.tag %></span>
                  </div>
                </td>
                <td class="px-8 py-6 text-right font-bold text-blue-600">
                  <span class="text-lg"><%= number_with_delimiter(account.value) %></span>
                  <span class="text-xs ml-1 opacity-70">WON</span>
                </td>
                <td class="px-8 py-6 text-right">
                  <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 font-semibold text-gray-700">
                    <%= number_with_delimiter(account.trophies) %>
                  </div>
                </td>
              </tr>
            <% end %>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>

      <% if @rankers.empty? %>
        <div class="py-32 text-center">
          <div class="text-5xl mb-4"></div>
          <p class="text-gray-400 font-medium text-lg">아직 등록된 유저가 없습니다.<br>검색을 통해 첫 랭커가 되어보세요!</p>
        </div>
      <% end %>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>